	* gdk/gdkrgb.c (gdk_rgb_try_colormap): Return gboolean, not gint.
	(#107664, Morten Welinder)
	
	* gdk/x11/gdkwindow-x11.c (gdk_window_get_deskrelative_origin): 
	* gdk/x11/gdkfont-x11.c (gdk_font_equal): 
