2003-01-21  Matthias Clasen  <maclas@gmx.de>

	Merge from HEAD.

	* gtk/gtktextview.c (gtk_text_view_size_allocate): Adjust the
	vadjustment value after changing its bounds.  (fixes #101963 and 
	#73562)

